@startuml geo-scoping-sequence
actor "Admin" as AD
participant "Geo Engine" as GE
participant "Security System" as SS
participant "Audit System" as AS

AD -> GE : Create Hierarchy Levels (State -> District -> Village)
GE -> AS : Log Hierarchy Config
GE --> AD : Levels Defined

AD -> GE : Create Geo Node (Village X in District Y)
GE -> AS : Log Node Creation
GE --> AD : Node Active

AD -> SS : Assign User to Geo Node (Village X)
SS -> GE : Validate Node Existence
GE --> SS : Valid
SS -> SS : Apply Scope to User Session
SS -> AS : Log Scope Assignment
SS --> AD : User Scoped Successfully

@enduml
